<li>Lilley, James D. "History and the Ugly Facts of <i>Blood Meridian</i>"; in <i>Cormac McCarthy: New Directions</i>; University of New Mexico Press, Albuquerque.</li>
<li>Owens, Barcley. <i>Cormac McCarthy's Western Novels</i>; University of Arizona Press, 2000; <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0816519285" class="internal">ISBN 0-8165-1928-5</a>.</li>
