<li>Shaw, Patrick W. "The Kid's Fate, the Judge's Guilt: Ramifications of Closure in Cormac McCarthy's <i>Blood Meridian</i>"; <i>Southern Literary Journal</i>, Fall 1997, pages 102-119.</li>
</ul>
